                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18300916-340-off1750 t18300916-340-cd1751"></join>, 3 sovereigns, 16 shillings, and 1 sixpence
            </rs>, the monies of 
               
                  <persName id="t18300916-340-victim2772" type="victimName">
                     William Lewis 
                     Thornborrow
                  <interp inst="t18300916-340-victim2772" type="surname" value="Thornborrow"></interp>
